			I'm not sure what people are complaining about...  Even with the cost of about 5 silver per pet, they are fully worth it.  While wizards have higher attack spells, they can't always get the spell off because of interruption.  The pet can take that monster off you.  Someone else mentioned that The fire elemental can only take on blues... NOT TRUE!  In CB I accidentally ran into a Legionnaire that conned red to me.  I killed him with my pet and HALF mana!  He gave me half a bbl of exp.  Each pet has their own strengths, and it's up to the caster to realize which situation is best for the pet.
