			Having a higher level Wizard, I quickly noticed the advantage that these pets allow.  Yes the Wizard class gets higher damage spells, shorter casting time and better damage/mana ratio, it is near impossible to solo with a wiz.  These pets more then make up for all of the above!  And for a few Sp per pet, they are worth it.  I have been able to solo yellows and reds with these, which is unheard of for the Wizards.  Good investment!
