		<td bgcolor="#DEDACB">
	
			<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
			Yes, the magician's pets can now use weapons.  I would not suggest giving them something really good, because you lose the item when your pet dies or you zone.  I personally like the earth elemental when I am fighting alone.  I am only in level 4 and I can wipe the floor with red centurians.  I just summon the earth elemental until it is yellow to me.  Then I let it attack the orc, it uses root, and I blast it with Burn until it is dead.  I tried this with any other elemental and they all died, and me soon after.  By the way, I would not invest money in the Elementalkin: Air.  That is the only one that totally sucks.  Sure it stuns them for a bit, but I mean, it does no dmg at all, and has low hps, so I use the elementalkin:earth all the time.  Enjoy!<BR>
<BR>
Sablibus<BR>
